;len, &laquo;Aw&shy;to&shy;mo&shy;bil ula&shy;gy ha&shy;kyn&shy;da&raquo; T&uuml;rk&shy;me&shy;nis&shy;ta&shy;nyň Ka&shy;nu&shy;nyn&shy;dan ge&shy;lip &ccedil;yk&shy;&yacute;an we&shy;zi&shy;pe&shy;ler na&shy;za&shy;ra al&shy;nyp iş&shy;le&shy;nip ta&yacute;&shy;&yacute;ar&shy;la&shy;nyl&shy;dy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&ouml;wlet Baştutany ha&shy;sa&shy;ba&shy;ty diň&shy;l&auml;p, aw&shy;to&shy;mo&shy;bil ulag&shy;la&shy;ry&shy;nyň işi&shy;ne yzy&shy;gi&shy;der&shy;li g&ouml;&shy;zeg&shy;&ccedil;i&shy;li&shy;giň &uuml;p&shy;j&uuml;n edil&shy;me&shy;gi&shy;ne, pu&shy;da&shy;gyň mad&shy;dy-en&shy;jam&shy;la&shy;&yacute;yn bin&shy;&yacute;a&shy;dy&shy;nyň pug&shy;ta&shy;lan&shy;dy&shy;ryl&shy;ma&shy;gy&shy;na, jem&shy;gy&shy;&yacute;et&shy;&ccedil;i&shy;lik ulag&shy;la&shy;ryn&shy;da &yacute;o&shy;lag&shy;&ccedil;y&shy;la&shy;ra edil&shy;&yacute;&auml;n hyz&shy;mat&shy;la&shy;ryň de&shy;re&shy;je&shy;si&shy;niň &yacute;o&shy;kar&shy;lan&shy;dy&shy;ryl&shy;ma&shy;gy&shy;na g&ouml;&shy;n&uuml;k&shy;di&shy;ri&shy;len anyk iş&shy;le&shy;riň ama&shy;la aşy&shy;ryl&shy;ma&shy;ly&shy;dy&shy;gy&shy;ny bel&shy;le&shy;di.</p>', '<p>T&uuml;rkmenistanyň Prezidenti Gurbanguly Berdimuhamedowyň 28-nji &yacute;anwarda sanly ulgam arkaly ge&ccedil;iren iş maslahatynyň dowamynda Mi&shy;nistr&shy;ler Ka&shy;bi&shy;ne&shy;ti&shy;niň &yacute;a&shy;nyn&shy;da&shy;ky Ulag we kom&shy;mu&shy;ni&shy;ka&shy;si&shy;&yacute;a&shy;lar agent&shy;li&shy;gi&shy;niň Baş di&shy;rek&shy;to&shy;ry M.&Ccedil;a&shy;ky&shy;&yacute;ew d&ouml;w&shy;let Baş&shy;tu&shy;ta&shy;ny&shy;ň tab&shy;şy&shy;ry&shy;gy&shy;na la&shy;&yacute;yk&shy;lyk&shy;da, Bal&shy;kan we&shy;la&shy;&yacute;a&shy;ty&shy;na bo&shy;lan iş sa&shy;pa&shy;ry&shy;nyň jem&shy;le&shy;ri ba&shy;ra&shy;da ha&shy;sa&shy;bat ber&shy;di.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iş sa&shy;pa&shy;ry&shy;nyň do&shy;wa&shy;myn&shy;da Ser&shy;het&shy;&yacute;a&shy;ka de&shy;mir &yacute;ol men&shy;zi&shy;lin&shy;de hem-de onuň &ccedil;&auml;k&shy;le&shy;rin&shy;d&auml;&shy;ki de&shy;giş&shy